A few opinions:<br><br>
It is not very often that you get to see the kind of thing that has transpired here, up close and personal. When you have the mind of a two year old in the body of an adult with developed language, the still unhumanized and uncivilized mind becomes at once very clear and visible. Scarey, isn't it?<br><br>
Blips in history, like Vlad the Impailer, Adolph Hitler, Joseph Stalin, and other like minded people, and their works, are examples of what power and control can facilitate for such a retrograde mind.<br><br>
I am gald to see, again, that no one took things too personally. It is the utter waste of time that is the real disturbing element to me. Life is short enough without wasting it on the contemplation of a corrupt mind and that which it spawns by asexual budding. Contemplation of maggoty roadkill is far more rewarding, and socially significant. I perfer to deal with real people on real issues. I don't think anyone would disagree!<br><br>
The actions that I see everyone taking individually in response to the threat of assault on a juvenile female is commendable. I wish everyone success. I have also taken an<br>
action on my own that will further enhance the positions taken by Anne, my Bro's, and everyone else on this site over the past year. <br><br>
It is hard for me to believe I have been on this site and continuously contributing for a year. I have survived everything that has been dished out, and I will continue to do so. The relationships I have established with the real people here more than outweigh the rantings of an insane mind. <br><br>
Here today, and here tomorrow!<br><br>
Art     
